### Editor UI Features
- **Blocks tab**: 2×2 grid palette (drag to add) + Row Layouts section
- **Layers tab**: Hierarchical tree with DnD reordering
- **Inspector**: Color pickers, sliders, alignment buttons, block-specific controls
- **Canvas**: Desktop/Mobile toggle, gradient background, card-style iframe
- **Toolbar**: Template name, undo/redo, gradient Save button

